<h2>Subst Handler Demo</h2>
The <a name='subst_demo'>subst demo</a> performs text substitution on node content.
<p>
</p><h3> Substitute a Pattern with Text </h3>

<b> Description: </b> Match on "10" and replace with "12". <br />
<br />
<b>Input: </b> &lt;subst match=10 result=12&gt;Columbus Day is October 10, 1998&lt;/subst&gt;<br />
<br />
<b> Result:</b> <subst match='10' result='12'>Columbus Day is October 10, 1998</subst>

<hr />
<h3> Substitute a Pattern with Text </h3>

<b> Description: </b>Match on "argu" and replace with "agre". <br />
<br />
<b>Input: </b> &lt;subst match=argu result=agre&gt;Argument between parties which argue&lt;/subst&gt;<br />
<br />
<b> Result:</b> <subst match='argu' result='agre'>Argument between parties which argue</subst>
